Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">第六步：申请商家入驻提交，等待管理员核对信息正确后为您开通店铺</span></p><p><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\"><img title=\"图片13.png\" src=\"http://xjd.taomas.cn/includes/ueditor/php/../../../bdimages/upload1/20160503/1462261471861797.png\"/></span></p><p></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '0', '1242577023', '', '0', 'http://', '');
