; LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">平台服务条款、平台规则。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">第五条</span></strong><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">&nbsp;<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">若本规则的规定同用户与</span></span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">平台签署的协议的约定相冲突，则优先适用双方协议的约定。协议中未约定的，则适用本规则。本规则尚无规定的，</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">有权酌情处理，但</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">平台对用户的处理不能免除用户应尽的法律责任。</span></p><p style=\"TE