span></span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">支付一定金额的违约金；</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">5<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">、关闭店铺：指删除商家的店铺，下架店铺内所有出售中的商品，禁止发布商品，并禁止创建店铺。</span></span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">第二节<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">市场管理情形</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">第二十八条<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">商家应积极提升自身经营水平，为买家提供优质的商品及服务。对于综合表现优秀的商家，</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(254,254,254); LETTER-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-WEIGHT: normal\">淘马鞍山</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY