 Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>1、任何非淘马鞍山商家出售的商品（序列号不符）；</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2、过保商品（超过三包保修期的商品）；</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>3、未经授权的维修、误用、碰撞、疏忽、滥用、进液、事故、改动、不正确的安装所造成的商品质量问题，或撕毁、涂改标贴、机器序号、防伪标记；</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs