 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2、大家电检测报告由厂家售后安排工作人员上门检测并开具。</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>3、建议家电商品外包装在收货之日起保留30天或更长时间。</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>4、玻璃制品和易损制品，只是产品局部损坏，可由厂商直接补寄即可，无需全部退回。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>5、个人护理类产品如遇过敏问题产生退货需要提供医院的相关证明，无质量问题不予退换。</span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>6、包装含防伪码的商品防伪码一经刮开不予退换货。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '0', '1365745287', '', '0', 'http://', '');
