de&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">提现到银行卡需要填写收款银行的收款银行名称，银行卡号和开户人姓名（信息填写要求都分别有注释说明）；</span></span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"20160407025957_99031.jpg\" src=\"http://xjd.taomas.cn/includes/ueditor/php/../../../bdimages/upload1/20160503/1462263301487033.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,254); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, &#39;Lucida Sans Unicode&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '0', '1365745306', '', '0', 'http://', '');
